ShardQuorum implements two public specifications from Blockchain Commons:

  * SSKR -- Sharded Secret Key Reconstruction (BCR-2020-011)
  * Bytewords -- Encoding binary data as English words (BCR-2020-012)

The cryptographic core in the :sskr module is an independent, clean-room
implementation written in Kotlin from these public specifications and the
SLIP-39 GF(256) Shamir secret-sharing scheme. It is not a copy or port of
Blockchain Commons source code (bc-sskr / bc-shamir); those projects are
acknowledged as algorithm references only.

